{"tid":1419030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武手足可唔可以聽我意見","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:59:04.000Z","uid":161592,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c93d4d1a5f4c9a7b279bcffc613036d4ca47366e","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:08:31.000Z","msg":"下次主攻既時候 <br />\n可唔可以搵班人頂住啲左膠？<br />\n可以係由啲女仔 或者年紀細既 攻擊力無咁強既人黎做<br />\n今日已經完全反映左膠點樣破壞運動 <br />\ne.g. 天水圍送頭事件<br />\n北角荃灣竟然放走黑社會人士<br />\n雨傘已經有眼睇如果左膠騎劫運動既後果啦<br />\n<br />\n再加上可唔可以有幾個手足保護記者<br />\n基本上今次運動去到依家<br />\n記者係被藍絲 黑警 黑社會 議員所針對<br />\n佢地每次直播都愈黎愈危險<br />\n我地應該盡力保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n而主攻力強即手足就全力進攻<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"6ff3f41a1eb508ec20873eef69da2e9f7e153891","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:09:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d8eb0a75516eec0c051f112d06ecb3013c8428c","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:10:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f8c12c6c672f16b699026685c14398a337184970","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:10:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1011fb6eb1e98c860d550fc3f353f443ad8d44d6","tid":1419030,"uid":266993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"左膠真係雷隊友<br />\n自己唔打 唔好阻止<br />\n佢一走就去斬其他手足"},{"pid":"de1481407c3d3bb8a1ea14ed1a94966995996316","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1011fb6eb1e98c860d550fc3f353f443ad8d44d6","tid":1419030,"uid":266993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:11:19.000Z","msg":"左膠真係雷隊友<br />\n自己唔打 唔好阻止<br />\n佢一走就去斬其他手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:12:42.000Z","msg":"打親佢又唔好意思"},{"pid":"715122776059032fc388f137ea0f496eef492cec","tid":1419030,"uid":161592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1481407c3d3bb8a1ea14ed1a94966995996316","tid":1419030,"uid"